# NovelClaw рџ¦Ђ

> Translation workspace for web novels (CN в†’ TH).
> Mika translates in chat; this repo is the persistent context
> (glossary, style, chapters) that keeps quality consistent across sessions.

## Principles

- **Transmittor, not editor** вЂ” transmit author's voice, don't "improve"
- **Completeness is law** вЂ” every word translated, zero gaps
- **Zero CJK leakage** вЂ” body text is pure Thai
- **Glossary is absolute** вЂ” locked terms never deviate
- **Validate before save** вЂ” tools catch errors AI misses

